                            },
                            {
                                "name": "license",
                                "value": "apache-2.0"
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    "description": "\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tDataset Card for Omni-MATH\n\t\n\n\n\nRecent advancements in AI, particularly in large language models (LLMs), have led to significant breakthroughs in mathematical reasoning capabilities. However, existing benchmarks like GSM8K or MATH are now being solved with high accuracy (e.g., OpenAI o1 achieves 94.8% on MATH dataset), indicating their inadequacy for truly challenging these models. To mitigate this limitation, we propose a comprehensive and challenging benchmark specifically designed\u2026 See the full description on the dataset page: https://huggingface.co/datasets/KbsdJames/Omni-MATH.",
                    "governance": {
                        "owners": [
                            {
                                "organization": {
